    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Everlife Classic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everlife is a fast-paced maze game where you must survive a mysterious realm that you have fallen into.  This version of the game is the original version, and it contains chapters 1 and 2.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/be1f730f4e71ace95dc9e1a81d8ede8a.poster.avif?t=1752647832\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/be1f730f4e71ace95dc9e1a81d8ede8a.webm?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/be1f730f4e71ace95dc9e1a81d8ede8a.mp4?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect the star and get out</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are tasked with collecting stars from a variety of worlds, and returning safely.  There are three different dimensions available, do you have what it takes to survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/1245598e2ecf63d457490a67a32d4506.poster.avif?t=1752647832\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/1245598e2ecf63d457490a67a32d4506.webm?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/1245598e2ecf63d457490a67a32d4506.mp4?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get running</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are never safe in the dimensions.  Dash at high speeds to the star, or to safety.  Outmaneuver the monsters and make split second decisions to stay in one piece!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/1125d291baf58629e249e43f159cb283.poster.avif?t=1752647832\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/1125d291baf58629e249e43f159cb283.webm?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/1125d291baf58629e249e43f159cb283.mp4?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are equipped with a special weapon.  With it, you are granted special abilities. Use them to defend, deter, and escape danger.  You'll start with only one ability, but you'll gain a new ability at the start of every level! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/4474d9f7c3aa54bce883598538c99aa6.poster.avif?t=1752647832\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/4474d9f7c3aa54bce883598538c99aa6.webm?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754480/extras/4474d9f7c3aa54bce883598538c99aa6.mp4?t=1752647832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional info</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For information on the current state of this game, please read &quot;Chapter 2 is now free-to-play + The future of Everlife&quot;</p>",
